==English==
===Noun===
'''älva'''

# A human-like creature from the [[Swedish]] [[mythology]]. She is often a young beautiful female, and you can sometimes see her dancing in the [[mist]]. 
A "älva" can be big as a human ore as small as a bug, she is dressed in white and will try to [[lure]] you in to her dance. But be careful; if you join her dance you will forget yourself and be just like her kind.